collections.name: Abstract photographic painting with city lights

collections.name: A to Z Edition - Minjae Lee
collections.description:
A to Z Edition is a visionary NFT collection by Korean artist Minjae Lee, reimagining his 2007–2025 traditional artworks for the digital age. Using pen, marker, colored pencil, and ink, Lee's iconic pieces are transformed into animated digital formats through Photoshop, Premiere Pro, advanced AI tools, various AI APIs, and personal training models based on his portfolio.

This collection envisions the future of traditional art, merging timeless craftsmanship with cutting-edge technology. By reinterpreting classical techniques in a modern digital context, A to Z Edition bridges the past and the future, offering an innovative perspective on how art evolves.

Featuring 10,044 NFTs derived from 31 original works, the collection spans 26 alphabet-themed lines, each with 372 NFTs. Beginning with the Origin, A, and B lines, additional releases will follow monthly. For updates, follow Minjae Lee’s official X account or visit NFT section of the website. Any Inquiries to info@grenomj.com.
